  <brief_title>Polydeoxyribonucleotide -Placentex Mastelli(Pdrn) for the Treatment of Diabetic Ulcers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diabetic Foot Ulcers and Use of PDRN (Polydeoxyribonucleotide -Placentex Mastelli) as a Treatment for Wound Healing.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
